headline: HD Extends Agreement to Offer KILZ Products, Boosts Customer Experience
summary: Home Depot's strategic efforts, including the 'One Home Depot' investment plan, appear encouraging. It extends its relationship with Behr Paint Company to provide KILZ branded primer products.

headline: Five Below Q4 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Comparable Sales Dip Y/Y
summary: FIVE's fiscal fourth-quarter results reflect higher year-over-year sales. However, the gross margin declines 70 bps year over year to 40.5%.

headline: Invesco Global Opportunities Fund Q4 2024 Commentary
